    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The new Halo-X is a long distance accuracy improvement tool that will help you level whatever you&#039;re aiming for. This 36mm rifle scope bubble level was originally designed for Leupold&#039;s Mark 5HD enlisted optic programs, this unique and precision-engineered level is now available for every day use. Made in the USA. Machined from ultra-strong 7075-T6 aircraft aluminum, this is our lightest and strongest scope mounted bubble level for rifles. Weighing less than half an ounce, and only 5/16&quot; wide, it&#039;s our most minimal level for crowded scope tubes with extensive vegetation</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Flatline Ops Halo-X Ultra Precision Rigid Scope Level Bubble (Multiple Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>The new Halo-X is a long distance accuracy improvement tool that will help you level whatever you&#039;re aiming for. This 36mm rifle scope bubble level was originally designed for Leupold&#039;s Mark 5HD enlisted optic programs, this unique and precision-engineered level is now available for every day use.</p>\n  <p>Made in the USA. Machined from ultra-strong 7075-T6 aircraft aluminum, this is our lightest and strongest scope mounted bubble level for rifles. Weighing less than half an ounce, and only 5/16&quot; wide, it&#039;s our most minimal level for crowded scope tubes with extensive vegetation.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>PRECISION ENGINEERED SCOPE BUBBLE LEVEL - Will fit either right hand shooters or left handed shooters; installs easily with all mounting hardware included</li>\n    <li>HIGH VISIBILITY ANTI CANT - Dual vial connection points and suspended bubble level with the reflective platform, allows maximum light refraction for enhanced fluid illuminated and sight acquisition. Jaw Bone barrel hinge point for easy installation.</li>\n    <li>SOLID, DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - Each of the bubble level for rifle scopes is machined from advanced 6061-T6 aircraft aluminum and then black hard anodized to protect it from the extremes of the outdoors</li>\n    <li>FEATHER LIGHT - Weighing less than half an ounce and only 5/16” wide, this is most minimal rifle bubble level for crowded scope tubes with extensive vegetation</li>\n    <li><strong>MADE IN THE USA - Bubble level fits 36mm rifle scopes; Material:</strong> 7075-T6 aircraft aluminum; Finish: Milspec Black Hard Anodized; Weight: .475oz; Width: 5/16” (.3125 inch)</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/covert_tactical/30036-HXB_flatline_ops_halo_x_detail_01.jpg\" alt=\"The new Halo-X is a long distance accuracy improvement tool that will help you level whatever you&#039;re aiming for\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 30036-HXB</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 783152253387</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Bubble Level Quality Specifications:</p>\n  <p>Vial-Bridge dual vial connection points and suspended bubble level with the reflective platform, allow maximum light refraction for enhanced fluid illumination and sight acquisition in all outdoor and harsh conditions Jaw bone barrel hinge point for easy installation Single top strap screw for ease of installation and access Ultra-light, high strength 7075-T6 aircraft aluminum Mil-Spec Type III hard anodizing for durability Built for left or right-handed shooters</p>\n  <p>PATENT-PENDING</p>\n  <p>MADE IN THE USA - Bubble level fits 34mm rifle scopes; Material: 7075-T6 aircraft aluminum; Finish: Milspec Black Hard Anodized; Weight: .475oz; Width: 5/16” (.3125 inch)</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The new Halo-X is a long distance accuracy improvement tool that will help you level whatever you're aiming for. This 36mm rifle scope bubble level was originally designed for Leupold's Mark 5HD enlisted optic programs, this unique and precision-engineered level is now available for every day use. Made in the USA. Machined from ultra-strong 7075-T6 aircraft aluminum, this is our lightest and strongest scope mounted bubble level for rifles. Weighing less than half an ounce, and only 5/16\" wide, it's our most minimal level for crowded scope tubes with extensive vegetation.",
